column15: (stringVal, <script>(function formCallback(activity, requestId) {    var setUpForm = function(page) {        var form = page.getChild();        form.listen('submitend', function() { activity.onSubmit(); });        form.listen('error', function() { activity.onSubmitError(); });    };    window[requestId] = setUpForm;})(activity, 'survey_request');</script>)

(stringVal, <script>window.get_help = function(page) {    var getHelpFlow = page.getChild();    if (typeof getHelpFlow === 'undefined') {        return;    }    getHelpFlow.getFormFlowStep().getEmbeddedForm()        .setContactFormCallback(function(form) {            form.setProductSpecificData(activity.getPsd());            form.listen('beforesubmit', function() {                form.setGcmRegistrationId(                    activity.getGcmRegistrationId());            });            form.listen('submitend', function() {                activity.onSubmit(form.getContactType(),                  form.getChatPoolId(),                  form.getCaseId());            });            form.listen('error', function() {                activity.onSubmitError(                    form.getContactType());            });    });};</script>)
